 006:     """Fast, re-entrant locking.
 007: 
 008:     Under uncongested conditions, the lock is never acquired but only
 009:     counted.  Only when a second thread comes in and notices that the
 010:     lock is needed, it acquires the lock and notifies the first thread
 011:     to release it when it's done.  This is all made possible by the
